! special
*.foreground:   #d3d0c8
*.background:   #2d2d2d
*.cursorColor:  #c25367

! colours
*color0: #161820
*color1: #947ca0
*color2: #298ca0
*color3: #597ba0
*color4: #9a6da0
*color5: #6f5ea0
*color6: #5ca097
*color7: #a08297
*color8: #7da5aa
*color9: #c87498
